description:
3+3 customizable screens with many widgets including:

 - calendars (Google);
 - notes/lists;
 - QuickContacts;
 - 6 different clocks; 
 - web search
 - weather widgets; 
 - RSS news (pre-defined or custom); 
 - app launcher with 3 different designs; 
and much more.

ActiveCard 2.0 works in portrait & landscape mode, has its own on-screen keyboard and comes with integrated on-screen notepad: "acWriter".

New in 2.1.0:
 • contact widget #3 redesigned;
 • RSS feeds auto update (Screen Settings);
 • webOS 2 ready;

*** Please watch AC 2.0 video preview before downloading. 
*** NON-US users: English only (including UI, on-screen keyboard, help, weather...)
